                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <blockquote class="help-testimonial mb-0">
                            <p>“I was copy-pasting ticket notes manually when a kid wandered too close to an active volcano. I hit <strong>Suppress in ConnectSecure</strong>, the lava paused, and the child waved. My manager said it was ‘probably unrelated.’ I know the truth.”</p>
