                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <blockquote class="help-testimonial mb-0">
                            <p>“Company review flagged an offline agent. I fixed it. That agent later became sentient, passed the bar exam, and represents me in probe-mapping disputes. We still use VScanMagic for holidays.”</p>
